title: What's your take on LSU's Top 10 showdown with Florida? | Tell us in 10 words
text:
Can a team stack more than 11 men in the box to stop Leonard Fournette? LSU's Heisman-winner-in-waiting did his thing against Saturday against Florida, as did fellow sophomore Brandon Harris in leading LSU to a 35-28 win.
Using just 10 words, share your thoughts in the comments section below, read what others have to say, and we'll post the best ones early Monday.
